{
  "stem": "19502.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The funniest part we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just-- they ran away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans were coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That just what we heard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe the parents knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But to us children-- don't forget those-- these children should have been seen but not heard.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if they had to say something, it was whispered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, it wasn't-- that we weren't allowed to hear those things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So that what we-- but they made sure that the refugees have food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They help-- they brought in food into the house, you know, the Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- so it wasn't bad under the Russian regime.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mind you, we were lucky because, you see, the rich people-- whoever was rich, whatever, you know, had businesses or so on-- they gather them and send them away in Siberia because they call them kulaki, kulak, bourgeois.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were lucky because according to them we were working class people because my father didn't own the forestry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was considered a working person so he was continued to work for them, for the Russians, you know, in the same places that he was working.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And lucky us, they didn't send us away in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they nationalized my grandparents' home in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a big home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's down there where it was the-- the office, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a very, very big home with fields and so on in the back of them there were fields.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my-- from-- from heartbreak, my-- my-- my grandmother died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my grandfather went to his son to [NON-ENGLISH] and died down there from heartbreak because they took away their home, the-- the Russian.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They nationalize it, you see, so that would--",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
